    "en": {
      "title": "A group of people who broke the warehouse of Mulleriya Hospital were caught",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Mulleriya Police say that they have arrested five suspects who broke into the East Colombo Base Hospital (Mulleriya Hospital) storeroom and several nearby houses and stole goods worth nearly 10 lakh rupees.",
        "They have been arrested as two suspects for breaking into the storage room of the hospital and three suspects for breaking into nearby houses.",
        "On the night of the 27th, the two suspects broke a window in the storeroom of the hospital and entered the storeroom and stole its property.",
        "The arrested suspects are residents of Mulleriya and Angoda areas aged 31 and 36, the police said.",
        "4 boxes of welding rods, 41 tared bars, 4 buckets of 4 liter paint, 5 kg gum bottles, 09 PVC pipes, 50 anchor bolts, 01 Kutin wheel pack, iron The police said that they found 500 and more washers and dryers.",
        "The police found these items while they were being sold, and many more items are expected to be found."
      ],
